# type

**Instance Property**

The underlying type of the sequence’s elements.

## Declaration

```swift
var type: MLFeatureType { get }
```

## Discussion

The sequence’s underlying element type can only be either [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType/string] or [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType/int64]. Use this value to determine whether to access [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLSequence/stringValues] or [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLSequence/int64Values] at runtime.
